These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  dressmaker, software-developer
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, water
2 different pets are kept: horse, rat
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the software-developer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Job   | software-developer    | dressmaker |
| Beverage         | water | sprite    |
| Pet     | horse     | rat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, sports
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, october
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, baccarat
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Movie-Genre      | sports  | satire   |
| Birthday   | october | april  |
| Cigar     | baccarat   | game |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, azalea
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, videographer
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, train
1. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4
2. the fisherman is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Flower         | amaryllis   | azalea  |
| Job   | videographer | fisherman  |
| Transport         | skateboard   | train |

