.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
2 different games are played: chess, poker
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, lavender
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, mystery
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
3. the person playing chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Game    | poker | chess     |
| Color     | lavender | grey |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | sports    |

 #################################

 
